{"tid":2298664,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"其實史提芬周當初點樣做到食神？","createTime":"2020-11-24T08:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T10:52:33.000Z","uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"55ee90a7b8b42007119ad6ea224623d4c1ef30bc","tid":2298664,"uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"電影無交待<br />\n其實佢本身識唔識煮野食？<br />\n如果唔識，點解唐牛會話：「你仲識唔識煮野食？」<br />\n用呢句推論咁其實史提芬周本身係識bor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a268350a0b86fcc479e9bff2347a75e86a5a5f5c","tid":2298664,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:10:07.000Z","msg":"你無睇佢最後咩<br />\n條友本身神仙嚟"},{"pid":"438dbf60a97117ec7be6dbc7a5f058c25785a551","tid":2298664,"uid":63843,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:12:13.000Z","msg":"使手段 靠關係上位 要表演煮野食就買通哂D人整水晶膠加雙氧水<br />\n佢本身應該唔多唔少都識煮 而且有天份 <br />\n但係為左賺錢扭曲左食既本意 煮野食冇用心 <br />\n去到最後先領悟到食既真意 只要用心 人人都可以係食神"},{"pid":"fb7d14a7a3d773f46073d16908deaa07f42ed524","tid":2298664,"uid":27247,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cRVgTsV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcRVgTsV.gif&h=e537426c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0V27fGi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0V27fGi.gif&h=6e38cee5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"788ae38f2e0d170014889849d1beba318eda1e76","tid":2298664,"uid":238415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"我係咁推拷<br />\n佢係識識地煮既...但應該唔係正規咁學過<br />\n又因為有d小聰明識走精面<br />\n屎忽撞棍咁比佢做左食神<br />\n之後就開始墜落<br />\n生意 &gt; 初衷...行事同思維越黎越無道德底線<br />\n淨係識諗計黎點解壓榨盤生意"},{"pid":"126043110b54611e9a6a806626b0635fb0cdf278","tid":2298664,"uid":119543,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08: